# DeepFang v0.1.0

**Goliath Docker-Compose Isolation Stack** — ZeroClaw sanitizer + DeepSeek-V4-Pro adjudicator + Moltbot worker, air-gapped with local Git mirror egress only.

[![Status: Alpha](https://img.shields.io/badge/Status-Alpha-red.svg)](README.md)
[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-blue.svg)](LICENSE)

---

## Architecture

```
┌──────────────┐     ┌──────────────────┐     ┌──────────────┐
│  ZeroClaw    │────▶│  DeepSeek-V4-Pro │────▶│   Moltbot    │
│  Sanitizer   │     │  Adjudicator     │     │   Worker     │
│  (Rust OS)   │     │  (Cloud API)     │     │  (Node.js)   │
│  Port 10932  │     │  Port 10933      │     │  Port 10934  │
└──────┬───────┘     └────────┬─────────┘     └──────┬───────┘
       │                      │                      │
       └──────────────────────┼──────────────────────┘
                              │
                    ┌─────────▼─────────┐
                    │    Supervisor      │
                    │  MCP + Dashboard   │
                    │  Ports 10930/10931 │
                    └─────────┬─────────┘
                              │
              ┌───────────────┼───────────────┐
              │               │               │
        ┌─────▼─────┐  ┌──────▼──────┐  ┌─────▼─────┐
        │ Prometheus│  │    Loki     │  │  Grafana  │
        │  10935    │  │   10936     │  │  10937    │
        └───────────┘  └─────────────┘  └───────────┘
```

### Network Isolation

| Network | Access | Services |
|---------|--------|----------|
| `deepfang-sanitize` | Internal only | ZeroClaw, Supervisor |
| `deepfang-adjudicate` | WAN (DeepSeek API) | DeepSeek Bridge, Supervisor |
| `deepfang-worker` | Internal only, no WAN | Moltbot, Supervisor |
| `deepfang-internal` | Internal only | Prometheus, Loki, Promtail, Grafana |

### Key Properties

- **Worker has no egress to WAN** — enforced at Docker network layer (`internal: true`)
- **Worker can only push to local Git mirrors** — Git repos volume-mounted at `/repos`, no internet on worker network
- **DeepSeek-V4-Pro is sole adjudicator** — all sanitized requests must pass DeepSeek before reaching Moltbot
- **ZeroClaw sanitizes first** — approval gates and tool receipts before adjudication
- **Supervisor observes all three networks** — MCP server for automation, web dashboard for human oversight

## Dependencies

- **[robofang](https://github.com/sandraschi/robofang)** — fleet orchestrator, Council of Dozens, DTU staging
- **[zeroclaw](https://github.com/zeroclaw-labs/zeroclaw)** — agent OS, approval gates, cryptographic tool receipts
- **[openclaw](https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw)** — multi-channel agent, Pi engine, sandbox modes
- **[DeepSeek API](https://api.deepseek.com)** — DeepSeek-V4-Pro cloud adjudicator

## Quick Start

```powershell
# 1. Clone & setup
git clone https://github.com/sandraschi/deepfang
cd deepfang
copy .env.example .env        # Edit DEEPSEEK_API_KEY
.\setup.ps1

# 2. Start the stack
.\start.ps1

# 3. Open dashboard
start http://localhost:10931
```

## Port Map

| Service | Port | Purpose |
|---------|------|---------|
| Supervisor API + MCP | 10930 | FastAPI + FastMCP 3.1 SSE |
| Dashboard | 10931 | React web UI for human oversight |
| ZeroClaw | 10932 | Sanitizer agent OS (Rust) |
| DeepSeek Bridge | 10933 | Adjudicator proxy to DeepSeek API |
| Moltbot | 10934 | Worker agent (Node.js, air-gapped) |
| Prometheus | 10935 | Metrics collection |
| Loki | 10936 | Log aggregation |
| Grafana | 10937 | Observability dashboards |

## MCP Tools

Connect Claude Desktop / Cursor to `http://localhost:10930/sse`:

| Tool | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `deepfang_status` | Health and pipeline summary |
| `deepfang_sanitize` | Run ZeroClaw sanitization on input |
| `deepfang_adjudicate` | Submit to DeepSeek for verdict |
| `deepfang_dispatch` | Send approved task to Moltbot worker |
| `deepfang_pipeline` | Full pipeline: sanitize → adjudicate → dispatch |
| `deepfang_audit` | Query adjudication log |
| `deepfang_agentic_workflow` | Multi-step goal via sampling |

## Integration with RoboFang

DeepFang is deployed alongside robofang on Goliath. Robofang's `federation_map.json` registers deepfang as a connector:

```json
"deepfang": {
    "enabled": true,
    "mcp_backend": "http://localhost:10930",
    "description": "Docker isolation stack — ZeroClaw + DeepSeek + Moltbot"
}
```

Start order: `robofang` → `deepfang/docker-compose up`
